{"id":"bd-phase1epic","title":"Phase 1: Core Infrastructure Setup","description":"Set up core CMS infrastructure including admin interface, OAuth, and Cloudflare Worker","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"epic","dependencies":[],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:00:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-adminhtml","title":"Create admin interface HTML file","description":"Create `static/admin/index.html` with Decap CMS v3.x from CDN. Remove Netlify Identity widget (using GitHub OAuth instead). Include necessary meta tags.","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase1epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:01:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:01:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-cmsconfig","title":"Create CMS configuration file","description":"Create `static/admin/config.yml` with GitHub backend pointing to `gerolori/gerosalorenzo.com-dev` (private repo). Configure for Cloudflare Worker OAuth proxy. Enable local_backend for development.","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-adminhtml","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:02:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:02:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-oauthapp","title":"Create GitHub OAuth Application","description":"Register GitHub OAuth app. Name: 'Decap CMS - gerosalorenzo.com'. Homepage: https://gerosalorenzo.com. Callback URL: TBD (depends on Cloudflare Worker). Document Client ID and prepare Client Secret for Cloudflare environment variables.","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase1epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:03:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:03:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-cfworker","title":"Create Cloudflare Worker for OAuth proxy","description":"Deploy Cloudflare Worker to handle `/api/auth` endpoint. Proxy GitHub OAuth flow. Return JWT tokens to CMS. Configure CORS headers. Can be in same repo or separate - recommend same repo for simplicity.","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-oauthapp","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:04:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:04:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-envvars","title":"Configure environment variables","description":"Set `GITHUB_CLIENT_ID` and `GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET` in Cloudflare Pages dashboard (encrypted). Configure Worker secrets.","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-cfworker","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:05:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:05:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-branchprotect","title":"Configure branch protection rules","description":"Optional. Protect main branch. Require PR reviews if desired. Enable automatic branch cleanup after merge.","status":"open","priority":3,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase1epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:06:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:06:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-phase2epic","title":"Phase 2: CMS Configuration","description":"Configure all CMS collections and widgets","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"epic","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-cmsconfig","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:07:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:07:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-blogcollect","title":"Configure blog posts collection","description":"Configure blog collection in config.yml. Folder: content/blog. Page bundle structure with path: '{{slug}}/index'. Slug: '{{year}}-{{month}}-{{day}}-{{slug}}'. Media stored with content (empty media_folder).","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase2epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:08:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:08:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-frontmatter","title":"Map Hugo frontmatter to widgets","description":"Map all frontmatter fields from archetype to widgets. Include: title (string), date (datetime), draft (boolean), description (text), taxonomies (list/select), display toggles (boolean), cover object, editPost object, body (markdown).","status":"open","priority":1,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-blogcollect","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:09:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:09:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-seriescollect","title":"Configure series collection","description":"Configure series collection. Folder: content/series. Page bundle with path: '{{slug}}/_index'. Fields: title, description, body.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase2epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:10:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:10:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-pagescollect","title":"Configure single pages collection","description":"Configure pages as file collection. About: content/about/index.md. Explore: content/explore.md. Search if editable.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase2epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:11:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:11:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-viewfilters","title":"Add view filters and groups","description":"Add view filters for drafts (draft: true) and published (draft: false). Add view groups by category, series, and year.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-blogcollect","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:12:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:12:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-phase3epic","title":"Phase 3: Media Management Setup","description":"Configure media management for page bundles and global assets","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"epic","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-cmsconfig","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:13:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:13:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-globalmedia","title":"Configure global media folders","description":"Set media_folder: 'static/images/uploads' and public_folder: '/images/uploads' for shared assets.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase3epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:14:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:14:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-pagemedia","title":"Configure collection-specific media","description":"Configure blog posts with page bundle media (media_folder: '', public_folder: '') for relative image storage.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase3epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:15:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:15:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-mediatest","title":"Test image upload flow","description":"Test end-to-end image upload. Upload while editing blog post, verify image in correct folder, verify relative path in frontmatter.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-globalmedia","type":"blocks"},{"target":"bd-pagemedia","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:16:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:16:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-phase4epic","title":"Phase 4: Local Development Setup","description":"Set up and document local development workflow","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"epic","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-cmsconfig","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:17:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:17:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-localbackend","title":"Configure local backend","description":"Add local_backend: true to config.yml. Document setup in README.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-phase4epic","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:18:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:18:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-localtest","title":"Test local development workflow","description":"Run npx decap-server. Run hugo server. Access CMS at localhost:1313/admin. Create test content. Verify Git commits.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"task","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-localbackend","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:19:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:19:00Z"}
{"id":"bd-devdocs","title":"Create developer setup documentation","description":"Document prerequisites (Node.js), step-by-step local testing, troubleshooting common issues.","status":"open","priority":2,"type":"docs","dependencies":[{"target":"bd-localtest","type":"blocks"}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T10:20:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T10:20:00Z"}
